item.title: CVE-2021-24143|2024-08-03T19:21:18.374Z -- unknown -- accesspress%20social%20icons
item.description: Unvalidated input in the AccessPress Social Icons plugin, versions before 1.8.1, did not sanitise its widget attribute, allowing accounts with post permission, such as author, to perform SQL injections.
